        <div class="span4">
          <h2>Effecient</h2>
           <p>Our online library management system takes all the unknowns out of the library equation and brings books straight to you without any intermediates. There
           are millions of titles that are available and paid for through your school. There are no late fee's since books are reclaimed automatically. Periodic updates keep users informed about the status of currently checked out books, as well as those they inquire about. There is no need to get up and drive or pay unnecesarry money. Better learning is just a click away.</p>
          <p><a class="btn" href="/static_pages/about">View details &raquo;</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="span4">
          <h2>Effective</h2>
           <p>Our OLM system provides a variety of tools for a more effective learning environment. This includes tools that edit, delete or add contents to checked out books.
           We also provide tools for sticky notes, tagging pages, highlighting, and searching books. OLM has all the advantages of traditional books, without the extra upkeep and costs.</p>
          <p><a class="btn" href="/static_pages/about">View details &raquo;</a></p>
       </div>
        <div class="span4">
          <h2>Reliable</h2>
          <p>One of the most important aspects of our website is reliability. Students need to be able to reference materials at all times and any gaps in these uptimes
          can be extremely detrimental. This is why we provide as close to constant up time as possible. Backup servers are used for updating and failover, while primary servers
          are constantly monitered for memory usage, security breaches and any other similar events that could compromise the site and data.</p>
          <p><a class="btn" href="/static_pages/about">View details &raquo;</a></p>
